Interface RecordStreamProcessor<SI,SO,DI,DO>

  • Type Parameters:
    SI - input schema type
    SO - output schema type
    DI - input data type
    DO - output data type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Converter

    public interface RecordStreamProcessor<SI,SO,DI,DO>
    An object that applies some function to a RecordStreamWithMetadata. For example, converters, quality checkers (filters), etc. are instances of this.
